<bibRefCitation author="Bogusch, P. &amp; Straka, J." box="[821,1096,513,539]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" pagination="1 - 41" refId="ref20454" refString="Bogusch, P. &amp; Straka, J. (2012) Review and identification of the cuckoo bees of central Europe (Hymenoptera: Halictidae: Sphecodes). Zootaxa, 3311 (1), 1 - 41. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3311.1.1" type="journal article" year="2012">Bogusch &amp; Straka 2012</bibRefCitation>
