<collectingCountry box="[603,698,549,575]" name="Portugal" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">Portugal</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Scheuchl, E. &amp; Willner, W." box="[743,1053,549,576]" pageId="23" pageNumber="224" refId="ref22731" refString="Scheuchl, E. &amp; Willner, W. (2016) Taschenlexikon der Wildbienen Mitteleuropas. Quelle + Meyer, Wiebelsheim, 920 pp." type="book" year="2016">Scheuchl &amp; Willner (2016)</bibRefCitation>
, no precise specimen information was provided and no specimens from 
<collectingCountry box="[626,721,585,611]" name="Portugal" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">Portugal</collectingCountry>
could be found in the Linz Collection. For now, its presence in 
<collectingCountry box="[198,293,621,647]" name="Portugal" pageId="23" pageNumber="224">Portugal</collectingCountry>
is considered unconfirmed.
